column5: Got out to ice shack on Edward Lake.Started early today around 2.Good action right away for 1/2 hr and that was it.stayed till 5 and only a couple here and there.but lots of fish on sonar.It does happen sometimes but highlight was catching a pretty good pike.Will have to try some diff times and see when it will be best.Days are longer now a bit mifht have something to do with it.
John I think the walleyes are taking a long rest they will come alive March 13,try not to disturb them John I'll wake them at sunlight in March,rod
Think i was to late yesterday Rod.That or the pike spooked them out.thought were coming on the 5 th.
Thanks Bill,that was a fun fight.She hit a 1/8 oz white marabou jig and a minnow.
